<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.9.1">
<l>kaḷḷammaṉam viḷḷumvakai karutikkaḻal toḻuvīr</l>
<l>veḷḷammutu paravaittirai viriyakarai yeṅkum</l>
<l>teḷḷummaṇi tikaḻumciṟu puliyūrccala cayaṉat</l>
<l>tuḷḷumeṉa tuḷḷattuḷu muṟaivāraiyuḷ ḷīrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who would worship [his] feet contemplating a way</l>
<l rend="indent">that reveals deception in your mind,</l>
<l>Think of the one who dwells in my heart and who is on a watery bed</l>
<l>In Ciṟupuliyūr where shine jewels which are cast up on the shore</l>
<l>Everywhere when the waves of the ancient ocean flood surge.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
